Description: Dual-pane file manager built with Qt5 and KDE Frameworks
 Gemini Commander is a modern dual-pane file manager featuring:
  * Dual-pane interface for efficient file operations
  * Built-in text viewer with syntax highlighting (KTextEditor)
  * Hex viewer for binary files
  * Archive support (zip, rar, 7z, arj and more via unar)
  * Device detection via UDisks2/D-Bus
  * Configurable keyboard shortcuts
 .
 Built with Qt5 and KDE Frameworks 5 for compatibility with
 Ubuntu LTS and Linux Mint.